Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H302498&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD Secret Police! Apollo Geist!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One of GOD's monsters, the invincible Achilles,\Nteamed up with the mysterious Apollo Geist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, the X Rider fell\Nin battle for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Encouraged by Tachibana Toubei, the X Rider\Nbegan training to create a new finishing move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Riders #1, #2 and V3\Nall overcame this training.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:02:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can get out of this pinch,\NI'll be a real Kamen Rider too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, think carefully about your opponent's weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember what his name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by that name...\NCould Achilles' weakness be his heel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles is an invincible hero of Greek mythology.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He had but one weak spot: his heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the myth, Achilles died\Nwhen that heel was struck by arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the origin of\Nthe term "Achilles' heel."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His Achilles' heel! His weak spots\Nare the jets attached to his feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't compete with his speed on the land...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I can take the fight to the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, lend me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Come at me like I'm Achilles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget... how you were breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy has guts.\NYou're a worthy foe, X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles won't have it\Neasy next time they fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Any problems with the human robots?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,None at all, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, just keep an eye out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles, the situation is beyond\Nsatisfactory. But you have further orders:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Monitor the X Rider. He must not\Ninterfere with our operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The human robot project's as good as\Nfinished, and the X Rider's all washed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So why would the Supreme Commander\Ngive me an order like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider is unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say, Apollo Geist!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only is the X Rider standing,\Nhe's training desperately to crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles, why don't\Nyou follow his example?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense!! You think the\Ninvincible Achilles might lose!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm off.\NI'll challenge him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist, why didn't you stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Chief of GOD's\NSecret Police, that's your prerogative!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon, Supreme Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But from my perspective, Achilles\Nis unable to make calm decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a poor fit for managing\Nthe human robot operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, I trust your analysis.\NResume preparations for the second phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki! You're safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, wonderful!\NWhat a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to Ooi Wharf if you want\Nthe cure for Miki's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles will be waiting,\NJin Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably caused by one of those darts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooi Wharf, eh? Achilles...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But your new finishing move will\Ntake another two days to perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound like you, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you tell the Kamen Riders\Nbefore me to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got me there.\NAlright, go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is GOD and Achilles I'm dealing with.\NHe won't just hand over the antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of trap has he set for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider won't lose this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki, bring Tachibana Toubei to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Jin Keisuke! Come out, Achilles!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,These human robots can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Human robots? That's what the virus does?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And only the antidote\Ncan return them to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward! Hand over the antidote!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke's-- no, the X Rider's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My life?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The chief and Miki take priority...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles, I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a brave one. But I'll have\Na little sport killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Show him a rollerskate hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him one lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If only Apollo Geist could see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, he must be dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Keisuke? Where's Jin Keisuke!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Achilles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's one-on-one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've beaten you before, and will again!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My only chance of beating Achilles\Nis to take the fight to the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Two-Step Kick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incomplete... But did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you... How did you know\Nmy weakness? X Rider...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't lost yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,D-don't shoot, Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to kill an ally!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! I am Chief of\NGOD\N's Secret Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're with those horrible Secret Police...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to serve him as you are, I execute\Nyou in the name of the Supreme Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Spare me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What a villain. I should cure the chief\Nand Miki while there's no one else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the X Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Prometheus, this is GOD's Supreme Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Supreme Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With Achilles' death, the human\Nrobot operation is discontinued.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The second phase is to train\Nthe human robots as saboteurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll then begin sabotage operations all over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me to your hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Apollo Geist?\NI'm quite the teacher, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You train GOD's Combat Agents.\NThis is the minimum I'd expect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Minimum...? Listen, none of those\Nhumans have even held a gun before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been working with them half a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This location is no longer secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Move all personnel out of the village at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider has the Dream Virus' antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl Miki is bound to have\Ntold him about this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt he's coming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So the X Rider's on his way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, leave no evidence here.\NMove out at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting so high and mighty...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider's coming, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:15:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know the villagers have been trained as Combat Agents...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a waste to move!\NI'll kill the X Rider right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As Apollo Geist suspected, Jin Keisuke was on his\Nway from Joutou University's labs to cure the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of GOD...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,With Achilles dead, are the\Nvillagers still human robots?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The villagers are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Could they be hiding from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you can come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Miki's mother here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright, I've brought the antidote!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, Jin Keisuke! I'm Prometheus,\Nthis operation's new commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so you're carrying on Achilles' work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a taste of my talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, fight, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The villagers are still...\NI don't want to hurt them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a dirty tactic, Prometheus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The surprises are only\Njust starting! Now, begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bamboo Spear Unit, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! You have to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your breath. These villagers\Nhave already become GOD saboteurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill Jin Keisuke! Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't fight you!\NI'll have to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke's fallen right into my trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready the landmines!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get. I'm going to find Apollo Geist.\NI want to see his face when he sees this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take your eyes off him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Prometheus?\NYou should have moved out by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to leave that village now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke snuck in, and I caught him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Jin Keisuke-- no,\Nthe X Rider we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to the village if you think I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There would be no point. The X Rider's\Nprobably cured the villagers already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn you, Apollo Geist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't be right.\NQuick, back to the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I knew everything would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to scare me like that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've come to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was never knocked out.\NI hypnotised myself to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'd let your guard down long\Nenough for me to cure the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what!? Assemble the saboteurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nicely done, chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, your daughter Miki's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you need to get somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:19:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Saboteurs!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Men!? Are you ignoring my orders!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Do you believe me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The villagers have regained\Ntheir senses and escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Apollo Geist will laugh if he hears\Nabout this... Let's go, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Prometheus Napalm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple Napalm Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That should finish off the X Rider-- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still alive, Rider!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Napalm Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.90,0:22:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's human robot operation has been crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But Apollo Geist is raring to take on the X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.10,0:23:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Money is vanishing from the city. Eerie lizards\Nare stealing money and killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With their water snake monster Hydra attacking\Nthe X Rider, GOD are causing societal upheaval.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.40,0:23:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out, Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Immortal Water Snake Monster, Hydra!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.30,0:23:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.30,0:23:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.60,0:23:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.60,0:23:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider